title: Jill of the Jungle Level Editor
content:
Does anyone know if there's anywhere where I can find a level editor for Jill of the Jungle? I have JillEdit, but it's a shareware version that can't edit the Objects/Sprites.

As far as I know there isn't any way for me to get the registered version as the company is (I think) in america and doesn't seem to have a website.

Alternatively, is there any way I could learn how to make my own level editor?

Thanks for your help.
